<h2>
  <svg style="display: inline-block; width: 32px; height: 32px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
    <path d="M7 11.5V14m0-2.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 113 0m-3 6a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v2a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0v-5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-6-3V11m0-5.5v-1a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v1m0 0V11m0-5.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v3m0 0V11" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  </svg>
  Bem-vindo(a), {{nomeUsuario}}!
</h2>
<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #3F51B5;">Estamos muito felizes em ter você conosco! Sua conta foi criada com sucesso.</p>
<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color: #2196F3; background: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);">
  <p style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 24px; height: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; color: #2196F3;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span><strong style="color: #333333;">Email cadastrado:</strong> <span style="color: #2196F3; font-weight: 600;">{{email}}</span></span>
  </p>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #3F51B5; margin-top: 32px;">Primeiros passos:</p>
<ul style="color: #555555; margin: 20px 0 30px; padding-left: 0; list-style: none;">
  <li style="margin: 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 20px; height: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Complete seu perfil e adicione uma foto</span>
  </li>
  <li style="margin: 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 20px; height: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Explore nossos recursos e tutoriais</span>
  </li>
  <li style="margin: 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px;">
    <svg style="width: 20px; height: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; color: #3F51B5;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <span>Configure suas preferências de notificação</span>
  </li>
</ul>
{{#if loginUrl}}
<a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">
  <svg style="display: inline-block; width: 18px; height: 18px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
    <path d="M11 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h14m-5 4v1a3 3 0 01-3 3H6a3 3 0 01-3-3V7a3 3 0 013-3h7a3 3 0 013 3v1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  </svg>
  Acessar Minha Conta
</a>
{{/if}}
<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="color: #777777; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.8;">
  Se você não criou esta conta, por favor ignore este email ou entre em contato conosco.
</p>